assessment.title: Living income assessment
assessment.description: This dashboard provides a comprehensive visualization of key insights from the Farmgate Living Income Price (LIP) assessment, conducted using the LIP methodology developed by Fairfood and Heifer International. Data collection for the living income study involved 270 farmers, out of which 260 provided the necessary information to calculate the LIP.
